position simplifies soon enough} 20. Nfd4 Bxg2 21. Kxg2 h6 22. Qb4 axb5 23. Qxa5 Rxa5 
24. Rxb5 Rxb5 25. Nxb5 Rd8 $11 {with a likely draw} *

