$1 {this is another small advantage of playing c6 - the queen can quickly get to b6 
to annoy b2} 5. Rb1 Nbd7 6. Nf3 h6 7. Bh4 g6 8. Bd3 Bg7 9. O-O O-O 10. e4 $2 {is 
premature} dxe4 11. Nxe4 Nxe4 12. Bxe4 g5 13. Bg3 f5 14. Bd3 f4 15. Bc4+ Kh8 16. Nxg5 
fxg3 17. hxg3 Qxd4 18. Nf7+ Rxf7 19. Bxf7 Nc5 $17 {and black has a material 
advantage} *

